    "description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >《KING’S ORDERS》简介</h2>在《King’s Orders》里，你将扮演一名中世纪的统治者，在欧洲版图上管理城市和军队。你需要写信给你的将军以下达命令，并根据收到的报告做出决策。历史事件将会重演，你要如何改变历史进程？建立延续数世纪的帝国霸业吧！<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1369690/extras/fd98c114bfee479be0040f0f8a0a180d.poster.avif?t=1754044892\" width=600 height=334 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1369690/extras/fd98c114bfee479be0040f0f8a0a180d.webm?t=1754044892\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1369690/extras/fd98c114bfee479be0040f0f8a0a180d.mp4?t=1754044892\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >中世纪欧洲</h2>从冰天雪地的斯堪的纳维亚到非洲海岸 - 开疆拓土，不断扩大战果，再现各经典的历史场景。每个历史场景都是对中世纪最关键的战役发起挑战，当然，战役的结果取决于你的指挥才能。百年战争、波立联邦-条顿骑士团战争、收复失地战 - 每场战役都可能是你最终全胜的关键。你是否能凭借过人的战略指挥能力，制定一项终极计划实现你的雄心壮志呢？<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1369690/extras/3547acdf704b75eee2fc278af87b89c5.poster.avif?t=1754044892\" width=600 height=334 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1369690/extras/3547acdf704b75eee2fc278af87b89c5.webm?t=1754044892\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1369690/extras/3547acdf704b75eee2fc278af87b89c5.mp4?t=1754044892\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >国王的策略</h2>和大多数实时策略游戏相比，《King's Orders》为玩家提供了更加身临其境的沉浸体验。派遣信使与部队沟通，下达命令并等待结果。记住，你的信使传递信息不仅耗时，还充满了危险。无法实时预览战斗加深了游戏的真实感。你可以通过报告掌握所有消息，并且只能依靠这些情报谋划战事，做出后续决定。<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1369690/extras/d35c62705455c92524433e3c068c3317.poster.avif?t=1754044892\" width=600 height=334 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1369690/extras/d35c62705455c92524433e3c068c3317.webm?t=1754044892\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1369690/extras/d35c62705455c92524433e3c068c3317.mp4?t=1754044892\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >分而治之！</h2>攻占各个城市，控制主要贸易路线。妥善使用获得的金币来换取各种机会。你想训练更多的部队还是专注于防御工事？成为什么样的统治者，采取何种经济管理方式，都由你自己决定。万事皆有因果，不得人心的决定可能会让你遭遇反叛。注意保持将领们的忠诚度和士气，才能让他们协助你管理人民。<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1369690/extras/a59a3ad543fc259b24c0fc6cad3dcf8f.poster.avif?t=1754044892\" width=600 height=334 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1369690/extras/a59a3ad543fc259b24c0fc6cad3dcf8f.webm?t=1754044892\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1369690/extras/a59a3ad543fc259b24c0fc6cad3dcf8f.mp4?t=1754044892\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>",
